snippet.textDisplay:
I think it’s funny how everyone’s mad about being let down by them unveiling their “new logo” I mean yeah it’s silly but those who were there at the complete unveil of the playstation 4 know that Sony doesn’t show their cards off right away. They waited for Xbox to unveil first, make a few huge anti-consumer mistakes like DRM and the inability to resell used games. And then playstation came in the next day with the full console reveal and blew everyone’s minds at how many tactical disses they threw at Microsoft. No DRM, the ability to resell, trade and let friends borrow their games, and at $100 cheaper than the Xbox one.
So, be patient. I’m sure when they do reveal the playstation 5 it’s going to be quite a show.
